575
00:38:34,910 --> 00:38:36,790
Everyone knows it.

576
00:38:37,070 --> 00:38:39,550
Why are you treating me as a stranger?

577
00:38:41,750 --> 00:38:43,150
Father is seriously ill.

578
00:38:43,790 --> 00:38:44,990
My brother is dead.

579
00:38:46,670 --> 00:38:48,670
