582
00:38:52,110 --> 00:38:53,950
Spare my life, Your Highness.

583
00:38:54,150 --> 00:38:56,510
It's just hearsay.

584
00:38:56,910 --> 00:39:00,700
How would a little hostage prince know about the affairs of the court?

585
00:39:00,700 --> 00:39:01,470
