593
00:39:20,030 --> 00:39:21,790
So I came to ask for rewards.

594
00:39:22,310 --> 00:39:23,430
What do you want?

595
00:39:24,910 --> 00:39:27,910
Wine, beauty, and a house.

596
00:39:28,310 --> 00:39:29,310
I'll accept

597
00:39:30,150 --> 00:39:31,350
