621
00:40:43,030 --> 00:40:44,150
Not a chance.

622
00:40:46,230 --> 00:40:47,090
Your Highness.

623
00:40:47,350 --> 00:40:50,990
He is a good pawn that

624
00:40:51,950 --> 00:40:53,350
